Laoke asked --<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> So what do you suggest as an alternative Sagemon? <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
FFA.  Yes, that has a lot of warts.  Believe me, I know what those warts are.  But the notion that someone is entitled to Ragefire because they sat on their butt in Skyfire for six days is just insane.<br>
<br>
