<br>
Laoke, if you or anyone else thinks that I'm happy about this, you're dead wrong.  If Verant had left the spawn along, I would have played the game in Sol B just like everyone else.  I can deal with a three-day spawn, and so can most other clerics.  By doubling the spawn time, Verant screwed us all over.<br>
<br>
